      "cooked": "<h2>29 Maj, 2017. Fotot më pikante të ditës:</h2>\n<p><strong>Kore e Veriut</strong><br>\n<strong>Kim Jong-Un vëzhgon testimin e një rakete të re me sistem kontrolli.</strong><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/8/8753d9efcf932b1d992d7841ca59a69ecb79bc04.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/8753d9efcf932b1d992d7841ca59a69ecb79bc04\" title=\"2500.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/8/8753d9efcf932b1d992d7841ca59a69ecb79bc04.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"528\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/8/8753d9efcf932b1d992d7841ca59a69ecb79bc04_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">2500.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1225×810 125 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p><strong>Matara, Sri Lanka</strong><br>\n<strong>Një stinë me shira dhe rrëshqitje toke ka shkaktuar të paktën 91 viktima.</strong><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/d/dfd672d8a5355e98d5b6440c7e97b3b40a0dca13.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/dfd672d8a5355e98d5b6440c7e97b3b40a0dca13\" title=\"2000.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/d/dfd672d8a5355e98d5b6440c7e97b3b40a0dca13.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"534\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/dfd672d8a5355e98d5b6440c7e97b3b40a0dca13_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">2000.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1225×818 255 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p><strong>Rio de Zhaneiro, Brazil</strong><br>\n<strong>Protestuesit mblidhen në një koncert/demonstratë ku kërkojnë zgjedhje të parakohshme për presidentin e ri të vendit.</strong><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/c/cf39856dcc2baa0b2c00097926f11522e123be43.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/cf39856dcc2baa0b2c00097926f11522e123be43\" title=\"6408.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/c/cf39856dcc2baa0b2c00097926f11522e123be43.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"532\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cf39856dcc2baa0b2c00097926f11522e123be43_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">6408.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1225×815 133 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p><strong>Bangkok, Tailandë</strong><br>\n<strong>Një vajzë e vogël ushqen një xhirafë në Botën e Safarit.</strong><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/c/cd0ca8c55f1ff5331984f3e2ed09e1e6e6b3f522.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/cd0ca8c55f1ff5331984f3e2ed09e1e6e6b3f522\" title=\"5265.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/c/cd0ca8c55f1ff5331984f3e2ed09e1e6e6b3f522.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"621\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cd0ca8c55f1ff5331984f3e2ed09e1e6e6b3f522_